description: Templated dashboard which provides an overview for your router/switch ports and detailed traffic statistics - customized for RIMS

targets.query: SELECT "in8s" AS "ifInOctets", "inUPs" AS "ifInUnicastPackets", "out8s" AS "ifOutOctets", "outUPs" AS "ifOutUnicastPackets" FROM "one_week"."interface" WHERE ("host_ip" =~ /^$host$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "if_name" LIMIT 1

list.definition: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM interface WITH KEY = "host_ip"
